title: december 17: a cancelled interview
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about a movie release that got cancelled, then uncancelled, with a lot of international drama in between. Afterwards, she talks about a record breaking rap album. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
